Class ModelLoaders

java.lang.Object
  pt.com.gmv.lab.implant.rendering.marker.ModelLoaders

public final class ModelLoaders
extends Object

Manages the registration of model loaders. Can load a model, with a given type, by resolving its association to a model loader.
